query:
insert into alpaca_activity
                (
                id
                , activity_type
                , activity_subtype
                , dtg
                , symbol
                , side
                , qty
                , price
                , cum_qty
                , leaves_qty
                , order_id
                )
                values (
                    $1
                    ,$2
                    ,$3
                    ,$4
                    ,$5
                    ,lower($6)
                    ,$7
                    ,$8
                    ,$9
                    ,$10
                    ,$11
                    )
